        "faq_mcUqEh": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What does the YarboCare™ Extended Warranty cover?",
            "answer": "<p>Coverage depends on the plan type:<strong>Extended Warranty (EW)</strong>Covers:</p><ul><li>Manufacturing defects</li><li>Electrical or mechanical failures</li><li>Performance malfunctions</li><li>Other issues covered by Yarbo’s standard warranty</li></ul><p><strong>Accidental Damage (AD)</strong>(Available as 1-year or 3-year add-on)Covers:</p><ul><li>Drops</li><li>Collisions</li><li>Impact damage during normal use</li></ul><p><strong>Not covered:</strong>weather damage, liquid damage, misuse, cosmetic wear, or unauthorized repairs.<br/><br/></p>"
