            "question": "How do I file a claim?",
            "answer": "<p>You can file a claim through the XCotton claims portal (link provided in your policy email):</p><ol><li>Submit order information, serial number, and a description of the issue.</li><li>XCotton specialists will review your claim and guide you through the process.</li><li>Repair or replacement will be coordinated by Yarbo and XCotton.</li></ol>"
